= hadoop-rubydsl

! now this module is reconstructing.. Please wait after year 2010. !

Enable to run Ruby DSL script on your Hadoop.

== Description

You can write DSL by Ruby to run Hadoop as Mapper / Reducer.
Depended on 'jruby-on-hadoop' project.

== Install

$ gem install hadoop-rubydsl

== How To Use
0. set HADOOP_HOME to your system. Run hadoop servers.

1. Upload your data to HDFS.
ex)
$ hadoop dfs -put apachelog inputs/

2. Run
$ hrd examples/apachelog.rb

